Baroin Says Collateral Deal on Greek Aid Is ‘Within Reach’

-- B y   G r e g o r y   V i s c u s i
-- 
2011-09-17T09:43:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-17/baroin-says-collateral-deal-on-greek-aid-is-within-reach-.html
French Finance Minister  Francois
Baroin  said the European Union is close to achieving an
agreement on demands by Finland that it be given collateral on
its loans to  Greece .  An agreement on collateral is “within reach,” Baroin told
reporters in Wroclaw,  Poland , after meeting with fellow finance
ministers from the EU.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gregory Viscusi in Wroclaw, Poland at 
 gviscusi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mark Deen at 
 markdeen@bloomberg.net  